Context: If you are a full-time Post-secondary or Apprentice student in your final semester of your program, you do not need to apply to graduate. Your information will be processed. However, if you are not in your final semester, you must apply to graduate through an online application. The deadline for application and other college news, upcoming events, tours, and more can be signed up for on the website. The contact number for inquiries is 416-415-2000 (TTY: 1-877-515-5559) and email is ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The information on the website is subject to change without notice, and students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
